  "mainHtml": "<div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-end gap-4 flex-wrap\">\n<div>\n<h2 class=\"font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface\">AI 模块配置</h2>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">与营销站「敏捷智造 AI 助手」对齐：管理工艺分析、智能报价、图生/文生 3D 与 DFM 检查五个模块。</p>\n</div>\n<button class=\"bg-primary hover:bg-surface-tint text-on-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm transition-colors flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">add</span>\n启用新能力\n</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">architecture</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary mr-1.5\"></span>已上线</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">工艺分析</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">模型与图纸识别：自动提炼推荐工艺、材料建议、关键公差与工艺风险，对话上下文独立保存。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">process</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">request_quote</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary mr-1.5\"></span>已上线</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">智能报价</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">成本与交期预估：结合材料、数量、表面处理与模型信息输出报价样例，正式报价仍需图纸与质量要求确认。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">quote</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">image</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary mr-1.5\"></span>已上线</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">图片转 3D</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">草图与照片建模：识别轮廓、孔位与结构，整理待补充尺寸，输出可继续用于 DFM 与报价的初始模型。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">image-to-3d</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">edit_note</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary mr-1.5\"></span>已上线</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">文字转 3D</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">自然语言建模：将用途、外形、尺寸与结构约束拆解为可确认参数，生成参数化 3D 草模。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">text-to-3d</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-surface-dim text-on-surface-variant rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">fact_check</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary mr-1.5\"></span>已上线</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">DFM 检查</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">制造风险建议：重点检查壁厚、孔位、倒角、装配间隙与后处理风险，输出可制造性建议。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">dfm</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex flex-col h-full border-dashed\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\">\n<div class=\"p-3 bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant rounded-lg\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">hub</span></div>\n<span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-label-sm font-label-sm bg-surface-variant text-on-surface-variant\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-outline mr-1.5\"></span>规划中</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">能力中心联动</h3>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-4 flex-1\">将 AI 结论关联营销站工艺 / 服务 / 材料 / 表面处理能力页，方便运营配置推荐跳转。</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant\">capabilities</span>\n<button class=\"text-primary font-title-sm text-title-sm hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\">配置 <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">arrow_forward</span></button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col\">\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-outline\">monitoring</span>\nAI 体验监控\n</h3>\n<div class=\"space-y-6 flex-1\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-end mb-2\">\n<span class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">工艺分析完成率</span>\n<span class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-primary\">92%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-high rounded-full h-2\"><div class=\"bg-primary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 92%\"></div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-end mb-2\">\n<span class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">智能报价 → /quote 转化</span>\n<span class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-primary\">14.8%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-high rounded-full h-2\"><div class=\"bg-tertiary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 15%\"></div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-end mb-2\">\n<span class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">游客额度消耗（示例）</span>\n<span class=\"font-mono-data text-mono-data text-on-surface\">3 轮 / 会话</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full bg-surface-container-high rounded-full h-2\"><div class=\"bg-secondary h-2 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 60%\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\">\n<h3 class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-outline\">account_tree</span>\n智能报价链路（对齐营销）\n</h3>\n<button class=\"text-primary hover:bg-surface-container p-2 rounded-lg transition-colors\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">edit</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 bg-background rounded-lg border border-outline-variant p-4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded shadow-sm px-4 py-2 w-48 text-center\">\n<span class=\"font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface\">模型 / 图纸 / 需求</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-px h-4 bg-outline-variant\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-4 flex-wrap justify-center\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-primary text-primary rounded shadow-sm px-3 py-2 w-28 text-center\"><span class=\"font-label-sm text-label-sm\">工艺分析</span></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-primary text-primary rounded shadow-sm px-3 py-2 w-28 text-center\"><span class=\"font-label-sm text-label-sm\">DFM 检查</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-px h-4 bg-outline-variant\"></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded shadow-sm px-4 py-2 w-48 text-center\">\n<span class=\"font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface\">成本与交期预估</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-px h-4 bg-outline-variant\"></div>\n<div class=\"bg-primary text-on-primary rounded shadow-sm px-4 py-2 w-56 text-center\">\n<span class=\"font-title-sm text-title-sm\">进入 /quote 正式询价</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
